    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c0a4d0a8e04ad46d9ea0688"
      },
      "index": 1,
      "text": "And it's highly questionable that the ones you have here now will achieve the job, <i>da</i>?\n\nUnless you have a surprise weapon to pull out of your hat... say like a big bomb that goes BOOM and radiates everything including 'Mechs.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "How would you know...",
          "conditions": null,
