      "comment": ""
    },
    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9c9df136e82cdb7431ea694c"
      },
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Until they decide to deploy their WarShip that is currently on the nadir jumppoint and the raiders are coming for the jugular. \n\nThey'll smash any organized resistance they can find before looting and killing everything else and terrorize the civilian population as needed.",
      "branches": [
        {
          "responseText": "",
          "conditions": null,
          "actions": null,
          "nextNodeIndex": 5,
          "hideIfUnavailable": true,
