    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cdfd1c659abb48128b5ad28"
      },
      "index": 8,
      "text": "No, that's what I saw them doing on Tortuga City.\n\nThe Council of the Damned couldn't stop them back then. They just picked us one by one until we realized too long that this wasn't one of our bands.",
      "branches": [
